('Silent E Magic', 'How E makes vowels say their name!', 'reading', 1, 12, '# Silent E Magic âœ¨\n\nWhen E comes at the end, the vowel says its NAME!\n\n**cap** â†’ **cape** (A says "ay")\n**hop** â†’ **hope** (O says "oh")\n**cut** â†’ **cute** (U says "you")\n**kit** â†’ **kite** (I says "eye")\n\nSilent E is magic!', 12, true, '[{"question":"What does silent E do?","options":["Makes noise","Makes vowels say their name","Nothing"],"correct":1}]');

