('Needs vs Wants', 'What we must have vs what we wish for', 'social', 2, 12, '# Needs and Wants\n\n**NEEDS** (must have):\nğŸ  Shelter\nğŸ Food\nğŸ’§ Water\nğŸ‘• Clothing\n\n**WANTS** (nice to have):\nğŸ® Video games\nğŸ¦ Ice cream\nğŸ New toys', 15, true, '[{"question":"Food is a...","options":["Want","Need","Neither"],"correct":1}]'),
('Handling Disappointment', 'It''s okay to be sad sometimes', 'lifeskills', 2, 12, '# When Things Don''t Go Our Way\n\n**It''s okay to feel sad!**\n\n**What to do:**\n1. Take deep breaths\n2. Talk about your feelings\n3. Think of something good\n4. Try again later\n\nDisappointment is part of life!', 15, true, '[{"question":"When disappointed, we should...","options":["Give up forever","Take deep breaths","Be mean to others"],"correct":1}]'),
('Cooperation', 'Working together is better!', 'lifeskills', 2, 12, '# Teamwork ğŸ¤\n\n**Cooperation** means working together!\n\n**How to cooperate:**\n- Listen to others'' ideas\n- Take turns\n- Help each other\n- Compromise\n- Celebrate together!', 15, true, '[{"question":"Cooperation means...","options":["Working alone","Working together","Not helping"],"correct":1}]');